@node "Document_0" "Introduction"
@{fg shine}MClock@{fg text} is a small BBS Cli-door to show the user date and time. It also shows
the city/board etc the user is logged into and it may display a small note.
I wrote it much justto write a clidoor but as it developed it's rather
usefull and I hope you will like it!
@endnode

